U.S. Wins Tax Shelter Cases Against Wells Fargo, Principal, Beal

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-10-04T15:51:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/u-s-wins-tax-shelter-cases-against-wells-fargo-principal-beal.html
The U.S. won three tax shelter cases
in opinions issued last week, the  Justice Department  said in an
e-mailed statement.  The cases involved claims relating to Principal Life
Insurance Co.,  Wells Fargo & Co. (WFC) , and a company formed in part
by billionaire D. Andrew Beal, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  